The evidence with the title 'What happens to the Democratic party after obama? ' says Jan 12, 2017  ... Most analyses overstate the Democrats ' down-ballot losses under Obama because they only start counting after he took office in 2009 .  ... The president 's party lost the same number of seats as Obama did under John Kennedy and Lyndon Johnson ( 39 ) and fewer seats under Dwight Eisenhower (26). 
